+# Local Capture + Server Analysis
+
+## Why this mode
+
+Remote MITM on the server can reach game traffic, but it often triggers:
+
+- `websocket close 1008 (policy violation): authentication failed`
+
+To keep gameplay normal, run MITM locally and only sync capture logs to the server.
+
+## Topology
+
+1. Local machine runs `xyzw_analyzer` proxy (`127.0.0.1:12311`).
+2. Game traffic goes to local proxy.
+3. Local analyzer writes `data/raw_capture/*.jsonl`.
+4. Upload those `jsonl` files to server for centralized analysis.
+
+## Local run requirements
+
+- Go `1.23+`
+- Analyzer repo on local machine
+- Local trusted CA cert: `ca/ca.crt`
+
+Run locally with passive capture mode:
+
+```bash
+XY_SKIP_UPDATE_CHECK=1 XY_CAPTURE_HOST='*' XY_PASSIVE_CAPTURE=1 go run ./cmd/xyzw
+```
+
+Notes:
+
+- `XY_PASSIVE_CAPTURE=1` avoids sequence/ack rewriting and keeps traffic transparent.
+- Keep game proxy set to local `127.0.0.1:12311`.
+
+## Upload logs to server
+
+Single file upload (today):
+
+```bash
+scp data/raw_capture/$(date +%F).jsonl xyq@172.26.10.61:/data/home/xyq/gongfa/功法/xyzw_analyzer/data/raw_capture/local-$(hostname)-$(date +%F).jsonl
+```
+
+Or sync whole folder:
+
+```bash
+rsync -av data/raw_capture/ xyq@172.26.10.61:/data/home/xyq/gongfa/功法/xyzw_analyzer/data/raw_capture/local-$(hostname)/
+```
+
+## Server-side quick check
+
+```bash
+ls -lah /data/home/xyq/gongfa/功法/xyzw_analyzer/data/raw_capture
+tail -n 30 /data/home/xyq/gongfa/功法/xyzw_analyzer/data/raw_capture/local-<host>-$(date +%F).jsonl
+```
